.TH SONDA 1 "@DATE@" "sonda @VERSION@" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
sonda \- network quality of experience probe
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sonda
.I command
.RI [ args ...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B sonda
is an experimental network probe that periodically measures DNS, STUN,
and other network properties, storing structured results in a local spool
for later analysis.
.PP
This tool is under active development and its interface may change.
For the full list of commands and per\-command help, run:
.PP
.RS 4
.B sonda \-\-help
.br
.BI "sonda " command " \-\-help"
.RE
